{"tid":1295532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際特赦組織會唔會幫到我地手？","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:57:38.000Z","uid":10392,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7cae2eac80c421eb22ac10c8d350ef82c9d2f3e0","tid":1295532,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"國際特赦組織簡介<br />\n......我們唯一關注的，是《世界人權宣言》及其他國際人權公約中所載的權利在世界各地是否得到落實。<br />\n<br />\n我們派遣研究員到懷疑人權受到侵犯的地區，完成調查後將結果或個案向國際社會公布，呼籲全球的成員一同行動，向侵犯人權者施壓，以遏止其暴行。 在政策層面，我們積極向各地政府進行遊說，使各地的政策及法律更能維護當地人民的基本人權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amnesty.org.hk/aboutus/introduction/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org.hk%2Faboutus%2Fintroduction%2F&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=f69ebba9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amnesty.org.hk/aboutus/introduction/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以點向佢地遞交證據，要佢哋調查香港黑警？"},{"pid":"e452ca9b20f79527e176ba0ecab83b2f24a61a05","tid":1295532,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2041f5061327317810017c0db4e51b07860dbf0","tid":1295532,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:09:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb7d6cfb5ac5ced8f1dd0ea22c2f9c0f8c165b00","tid":1295532,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dde1b7533a79832481b574192143d93a9112700","tid":1295532,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d6aa4183510ad7f7bfd11f9c593e81198ab153","tid":1295532,"uid":31496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"佢哋都有望住㗎喇，有多啲資料冇壞嘅。"},{"pid":"567c446a737f